284
00:17:11,079 --> 00:17:11,910
Indeed.

285
00:17:14,589 --> 00:17:16,109
It's just like a dream.

286
00:17:19,819 --> 00:17:20,819
There are sweet dreams,

287
00:17:21,530 --> 00:17:22,589
and there are nightmares.

288
00:17:23,920 --> 00:17:25,390
Isn't life just like that?

289
00:17:28,160 --> 00:17:30,230
Since ancient times, being too sentimental only leads to regret.

290
00:17:31,560 --> 00:17:34,670
The sweetest dreams are always the easiest to wake from.

291
00:17:36,790 --> 00:17:38,270
I'm back to life now!

292
00:17:40,490 --> 00:17:41,190
It's weird.

293
00:17:41,210 --> 00:17:42,710
