299
00:17:53,370 --> 00:17:54,470
Where's my mask?

300
00:17:54,900 --> 00:17:56,430
Can't teach without your mask?

301
00:17:56,750 --> 00:17:58,400
Of course, the atmosphere isn't right without it.

302
